## Personal Cloud Bots
<match bot.**>
  type s3

  aws_key_id <%= @s3_key %>
  aws_sec_key <%= @s3_secret_key %>
  s3_bucket <%= @s3_bucket %>
  s3_endpoint s3.amazonaws.com
  path <%= @s3_log_path %>

  time_slice_format %Y%m%d%H%M%S

  buffer_path /var/log/td-agent/s3
  buffer_chunk_limit 256m
</match>

